            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>tomato stock </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>Amatriciana sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
