        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained orecchiette </strong>to the pan and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>tomato & bacon Amatriciana sauce with fresh orecchiette</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
