    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tomato & bacon Amatriciana sauce with fresh orecchiette</strong> topped with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
